               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290910-273-cd1506" type="crimeDate">9th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-273-off1505 t18290910-273-cd1506"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 5s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290910-273-victim2568" type="victimName">
                           Robert 
                           Howson
                        <interp inst="t18290910-273-victim2568" type="surname" value="Howson"></interp>
